entries.arrival_phase_1: Scanning system for the emissary's ship. Stand by to proceed with destroying his ship.
entries.arrival_phase_2: Nav location to the target vessel has been located. Proceed with extreme prejudice.
entries.assassinate_success: Good work, pilot. Without that rebel officer working as a go between, Nym is likely to pull out of the system. Return to your commander.
entries.destroy_escort: Just to be safe take out the escort fighters as well. We cannot be too careful with this situation.
entries.escort_remaining: pcontrast1 Tactical Computer:pcontrast3 <%DI escort fighters remaining.>
entries.escort_wiped_out: pcontrast1 Tactical Computer:pcontrast3 <Enemy escort fighter eliminated.>
entries.failed_escape: You let him get away! Now we have to wait for another opportunity to try to break the alliance. Report your failure to your commander.
entries.quest_escort_d: Make sure that all of the emissary's escort fighters are destroyed as well. Once you have completed this task return to your commander.
entries.quest_location_d: Remain in the Yavin system and eliminate the emissary. It would seem that the emissary is attempting to flee the system.
entries.quest_target_d: Intercept the Rebel emissary in the Yavin system and kill him. Without his influence it is almost assured that Nym will withdraw his support.
entries.title: Yavin System: Eliminate the Rebel Emissary
entries.title_d: Eliminate the Rebel emissary as he moves through the Yavin system. With the information on the attack gathered from the freighter, Black Epsilon has managed to determine where the Rebel emissary is. Without the Emissary the Rebels will have a hard time keeping Nym's support.
